simplesect.para:
All coordinates are internally handled as CWRUtil::Q5 which means that floating point values are rounded down to a fixed number of binary digits, for example: Lineline;
line.setStart(1.1f,1.1f);//Willuse(35/32,35/32)=(1.09375f,1.09375f)
intx,y;
line.getStart(&amp;x,&amp;y);//Willreturn(1,1)
.
